                "name": "Before Combat",
                "text": " The paragon drinks her <i>potion of bear\u2019s endurance</i>, <i>potion of bull\u2019s strength</i>, and fervor juice."
            },
            {
                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "tactic",
                "name": "During Combat",
                "text": " Obsessed with martial prowess and proving herself superior to her enemies, the paragon seeks out a challenging opponent to square off against in one-onone combat. If faced with many foes of equal ability, she rushes from one to another, using Spring Attack to get their attention and draw them to her."
            },
